            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="https://pittsburgh.craigslist.org/apa/d/pittsburgh-beautiful-two-bed-855-month/7511530599.html"></div>
        </div>
Beautiful two bedroom apartment for $855/month plus electric available for a July move in. Located in the heart of Castle Shannon at our Hoodridge Court location. The  bedroom is around 733 sq. feet. Units have wall to wall carpeting, ceramic tile bath, and come equipped with a stove, oven, and a refrigerator. The building comes equipped with coin operated laundry which costs $1.25 per load and an intercom entry system. Building also has off street parking for $40/month and garage parking for $50/month. Tenants are responsible for paying the electric and cable/internet. Union Real estate is responsible for paying the gas, trash, water, and sewage.<br>
<br>
Application fees:<br>
$45 per person for credit/background check plus security deposit in the amount of one month's rent.<br>
<br>
Building is managed by Union Real Estate  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/pit/apa/7511530599/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
